---
title: Creamy Truffle, Mushroom & Bacon Fettuccine with Pine Nut Pangrattato & Rocket Salad
description: This fettuccine dish pairs the earthy flavour of mushroom and truffle with an easy creamy sauce. The side salad balances the
richness of the pasta with peppery rocket, sweet pear and sharp Parmesan.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/creamy-truffle-mushroom-bacon-fettuccine-eb58ecc4.jpg
